sentences: Mark Morgan (born October 22, 1961) is an American musician and score composer for video games, television and films.
He is known for his work in Fallout, Fallout 2 and Planescape: Torment, and for being a former member of Starship.
In 1988, he joined Starship on keyboards, played on the Love Among the Cannibals album with the band, and toured with them until 1990.
